# Default Triton GEMM configs for consumer Blackwell GPUs (SM 12.0).
# Generated by exhaustive autotuning on RTX 5090 (170 SMs, 2.467 GHz,
# 1792 GB/s memory bandwidth, 96 MB L2 cache).
# Workloads: ~300 operations including fused linear layers (matmul + bias
# + activation), attention projections, SwiGLU MLP, attention scores,
# shapes from triton_gemm_fusion_test.cc, and pure matmuls in f32/f16/bf16.
